TensorFlow and OpenCV for plant disease detection. We’ll utilize a pre-trained model such as MobileNetV2 (available as an open-source model), and ensure proper error handling and modularity.


project_root/
│
├── model/
│   ├── __init__.py  # Makes model a package
│   └── load_model.py  # Model loading functionality
│
├── utils/
│   ├── __init__.py  # Makes utils a package
│   └── image_preprocessing.py  # Image preprocessing utilities
│
├── main.py  # Main application
